Evaluation of the diagnostic performances of the 3 commercial MERS-CoV rRT-PCR assays showed the TIB MolBiol® LightMix assays as having the best clinical sensitivity, followed by the Seegene and GeneSig® assays (Table 2
). Comparative cycle threshold (CT) values are detailed in Table 3
, except for the Anyplex™ Seegene assay which provided only qualitative detection. All internal controls (where applicable) were valid, with minimal CT variations.
